6: Hoo, boy... Here we go again.
10: Oh no! Is everything all right?
15:
You don't have to do that—careful!
You wouldn't want to cut yourself on
the glass.
18:
Don't you worry. This isn't my first
time picking up broken pieces like
this, and it won't be the last!
21:
In my case, it's because I'm so
awfully clumsy. But for you, Alk, it's
different.
25:
You're pushing yourself to the brink
of exhaustion!
28:
That's a bit of a stretch, don't you
think?
32:
Oh, and you don't even realize you're
doing it! This is most troubling…
36:
Alk, are you aware of how hard
you're working yourself?
40:
I mean, I don't do that much... I
usually just explore the
Kaleidoscope and cook.
42:
You also clean, do laundry, do
various errands, and perform item
inspections too, right?
45:
To put it bluntly, you're overworking
yourself!
49:
I don't think I'm doing THAT much
work.
52:
You're so kind, Alk—so dedicated to
helping everyone else.
54:
But it's important that you're
dedicated to helping yourself too!
57:
It's no big deal, really. Someone's
gotta do it, right?
60:
You're right. I'm not saying that you
should stop everything that you're
doing! Especially cooking—that
seems to be very important to you!
63:
But sometimes you need to know
when to recharge. If you don't learn
to say "that's enough for now", you'll
always blame yourself for not doing
more!
66:
So please, Alk...
Slack off for once!
69:
Just for a few days… or maybe even
just today!
Forget everything and just relax!
73:
Fine. I suppose I could take it
easy—just for today though, okay?
80:
How about I also offer you some of
my special healing treatment while
we're at it?
85:
Scented oils?
They're so... fragrant... It's nice…
88:
Hehe. One whiff and you already feel
relaxed, right?
90: Okay, close your eyes and relax.
92:
Don't worry... Just leave everything
to me…
97:
I don't think... I'm kind...
Or anything like that…
99: But if I don't help, I feel... anxious…
110:
Good morning!
How are you feeling?
115:
Whoa... It feels like a huge weight's
been lifted from my mind. I must've
been pretty tired after all.
120: Hehe. I'm just glad I was able to help!
127:
I guess we all needed a little extra
shut-eye, huh?
130:
Everyone else said the exact same
thing when they saw you sleeping.
139:
Knowing when not to work hard is
often just as important as working
hard. Wouldn't you agree?
141:
Some people might scold you for
being lazy. But honestly, who cares?
Indulging yourself every once in a
while is just the greatest!
142:
My dream is to one day bring peace
to the whole world with the power of
relaxation! Wouldn't that be
amazing?
145:
Ahaha... I think I'd be on board with
that, honestly.
149:
*yawn*
Harlisha, would you mind... if I took
another nap?
152:
Of course not! I'll make sure to add
some more oil to the pot later on
then.
156:
Thank you. But, Harlisha, make sure
you get some rest too, all right?
170:
You truly are a kind person, Alk. Of
that I have no doubt.
